*[[1637]] &amp;ndash; [[Nicolas-Claude Fabri de Peiresc]], French astronomer (b. 1580)
*[[1643]] &amp;ndash; [[John Hampden]], English politician (b. 1595)
*[[1766]] &amp;ndash; [[Adrien Maurice de Noailles]], French soldier (b. 1678)
*[[1778]] &amp;ndash; [[Pieter Burman the Younger]], Dutch philologist (b. 1714)
*[[1803]] &amp;ndash; [[Matthew Thornton]], Irish-American politician, signer of the [[United States Declaration of Independence]] (b. 1714)
*[[1817]] &amp;ndash; [[Thomas McKean]], American lawyer and politician (b. 1734)
*[[1835]] &amp;ndash; [[Andreas Vokos Miaoulis]], Greek admiral and politician (b. 1769)
*[[1894]] &amp;ndash; [[Marie François Sadi Carnot]], French statesman (b. 1837)
*[[1908]] &amp;ndash; [[Grover Cleveland]], American politician, 22nd and 24th [[President of the United States]] (b. 1837)
*[[1909]] &amp;ndash; [[Sarah Orne Jewett]], American writer (b. 1849)
*[[1922]] &amp;ndash; [[Walther Rathenau]], German industrialist, politician, and writer, [[Foreign Minister of Germany]] (b. 1867)
*[[1931]] &amp;ndash; [[Otto Mears]], Russian-American railroad builder and entrepreneur (b. 1840)
*  1931   &amp;ndash; [[Xiang Zhongfa]], Chinese politician, 2nd [[General Secretary of the Communist Party of China]] (b. 1880)
*[[1935]] &amp;ndash; [[Carlos Gardel]], Argentine singer-songwriter and actor (b. 1890)
*[[1946]] &amp;ndash; [[Louise Whitfield Carnegie]], American philanthropist (b. 1857)
*[[1947]] &amp;ndash; [[Emil Seidel]], American politician, [[Mayor of Milwaukee]] (b. 1864)
*[[1968]] &amp;ndash; [[Tony Hancock]], English comedian and actor (b. 1924)
*[[1976]] &amp;ndash; [[Imogen Cunningham]], American photographer (b. 1883)
*[[1977]] &amp;ndash; [[André-Gilles Fortin]], Canadian politician (b. 1943)
*[[1978]] &amp;ndash; [[Robert Charroux]], French writer (b. 1909)
*[[1984]] &amp;ndash; [[Clarence Campbell]], Canadian 3rd president of the [[National Hockey League]] (b. 1905)
*[[1987]] &amp;ndash; [[Jackie Gleason]], American actor and singer (b. 1916)
*[[1989]] &amp;ndash; [[Hibari Misora]], Japanese singer and actress (b. 1937)
*[[1991]] &amp;ndash; [[Sumner Locke Elliott]], Australian-American novelist (b. 1917)
*  1991   &amp;ndash; [[Rufino Tamayo]], Mexican painter (b. 1899)
*[[1997]] &amp;ndash; [[Don Hutson]], American football player (b. 1913)
*  1997   &amp;ndash; [[Brian Keith]], American actor (b. 1921)
*[[2000]] &amp;ndash; [[Vera Atkins]], Romanian-English intelligence officer (b. 1908)
*  2000   &amp;ndash; [[Rodrigo Bueno]], Argentine singer-songwriter {b. 1973}
*  2000   &amp;ndash; [[David Tomlinson]], English actor (b. 1917)
*[[2002]] &amp;ndash; [[Pierre Werner]], Luxembourgian politician, 21st [[Prime Minister of Luxembourg]] (b. 1913)
*[[2003]] &amp;ndash; [[Vladimir Garin]], Russian actor (b. 1987)
*[[2004]] &amp;ndash; [[Ifigeneia Giannopoulou]], Greek songwriter and author (b. 1957)
