*[[2009]] &amp;ndash; [[Roméo LeBlanc]], Canadian journalist and politician, 25th [[Governor General of Canada]] (b. 1927)
*  2009   &amp;ndash; [[Ed Thomas]], American educator and football coach (b. 1951)
*[[2011]] &amp;ndash; [[Tomislav Ivić]], Croatian footballer and manager (b. 1933)
